Invocation Name: fort wayne guide
des: The Fort Wayne Guide provides local attractions and things to do for those new to Fort Wayne, or looking to discover what this town has to offer. No matter what your tastes, the Fort Wayne Guide will help you find a fun way to spend a day with family and friends and discover what is available to you in this great city.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
